{"type":"message","id":"2a8f2d77","parentId":"31dba827","timestamp":"2026-02-23T06:02:19.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that IDENTITY.md and USER.md are still in their template state - this is a fresh workspace. The MEMORY.md file has some basic context about Google Sheets (inventory and cleaning tabs).\n\nSince I don't have an established persona yet (IDENTITY.md is blank), I should:\n1. Check if BOOTSTRAP.md exists - if so, I should follow its instructions\n2. Otherwise, greet them naturally and start figuring out who I am\n\nLet me check for BOOTSTRAP.md","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-aa79ecd2e509c57a","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\BOOTSTRAP.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":14521,"output":247,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14768,"cost":{"input":0.0055179800000000005,"output":0.0004199,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00593788}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771826508829}}
{"type":"message","id":"54735938","parentId":"2a8f2d77","timestamp":"2026-02-23T06:02:19.058Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-aa79ecd2e509c57a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When You're Done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771826539053}}
{"type":"message","id":"a90e1749","parentId":"54735938","timestamp":"2026-02-23T06:02:23.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! BOOTSTRAP.md exists, which means I should follow its instructions. This is a fresh setup, so I need to:\n\n1. Start a conversation to figure out who I am and who they are\n2. Be conversational, not robotic\n3. Follow the bootstrap process to set up my identity\n\nThe instructions say to start with something like \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\" and then figure it out together.\n\nI should be natural and conversational. Since I notice they have a Google Sheets setup (inventory and cleaning), I could reference that naturally in the conversation.\n\nLet me greet them in a friendly, casual way.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\n\nI noticed you've got some Google Sheets set up for inventory and cleaning — already getting organized, huh? Let me know what you'd like to call me, and we can figure out the rest from there."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":1121,"output":356,"cacheRead":13824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15301,"cost":{"input":0.00042598,"output":0.0006052,"cacheRead":0.00262656,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00365774}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771826539060}}
