{"type":"message","id":"d576ff5a","parentId":"2c3aa9ab","timestamp":"2026-02-23T06:13:30.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! I can see that:\n\n1. There's a `pdf-cli.js` script that already has dummy data set up and is ready to run\n2. The script generates a sublease agreement PDF with the dummy data\n3. It includes letterhead (the `true` parameter)\n4. It saves the PDF to a file with the tenant's name\n\nThe dummy data in the script is:\n- tenantName: 'John Doe'\n- sublessorName: 'Jane Smith'\n- propertyAddress: '123 Main St, New York, NY 10018'\n- rent: '2500'\n- proRateRent: '500'\n- securityDeposit: '2500'\n- leaseStartDate: '2026-03-01'\n- leaseEndDate: '2027-02-28'\n- agreementDate: '2026-02-23'\n\nI just need to run this script to generate the PDF.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2517","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node \"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\pdf-generator\\scripts\\pdf-cli.js\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":3368,"output":398,"cacheRead":16320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20086,"cost":{"input":0.00127984,"output":0.0006766,"cacheRead":0.0031008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005057239999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771827194587}}
