{"type":"message","id":"7107bef5","parentId":"1f941e11","timestamp":"2026-02-23T06:13:49.334Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great! The PDF has been generated successfully. It's 2.8MB in size and was created just now. Let me provide a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Done! Generated a sublease agreement PDF with dummy data:\n\n**File:** John Doe Sublease Agreement.pdf  \n**Size:** 2.8 MB  \n**Location:** `skills/pdf-generator/`\n\nThe dummy data includes:\n- Tenant: John Doe\n- Sublessor: Jane Smith\n- Property: 123 Main St, New York, NY 10018\n- Rent: $2,500/month (with $500 prorated for first month)\n- Security Deposit: $2,500\n- Lease: March 1, 2026 – February 28, 2027\n- Agreement Date: February 23, 2026\n\nWant to generate another with different data, or need the PDF sent somewhere?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":97,"output":216,"cacheRead":19968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20281,"cost":{"input":0.00003686,"output":0.0003672,"cacheRead":0.00379392,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0041979800000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771827218103}}
